  "title": "Moroccan Spice Moroccan Chewy Umami Sellou",
  "description": "A weeknight Moroccan dish featuring brown sugar, dashi-extract, and a unique blend of spices, all wrapped in the traditional form of sellou, served in a scallop shell.",
