  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the slivered almonds and fry until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove the almonds from the skillet and set aside on a paper towel-lined plate.",
    "In the same skillet, combine the brown sugar, dashi-extract, water, cinnamon, ginger, smoked paprika, and sea salt. ",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, stirring occasionally.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, or until the mixture has thickened slightly.",
    "Stir in the fried almonds, dried dates, and pitted prunes (if using).",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, or until the sellou has reached your desired consistency.",
    "Spoon the sellou into preheated scallop shells and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve immediately, and enjoy!"
  ],
